  <?dbhtml filename="xf86driproto.html"?>

  <title>xf86driproto-&xf86driproto-version;</title>

  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction</title>

    <para>
      This extension defines a protocol to allow user applications to access the
      video hardware without requiring data to be passed through the X server.
    </para>

